    "title": "SeaKing Bait Board B03 (830mm x 430mm) & 2 Game Rated Rod Holders",
    "body_html": "<p dir=\"ltr\">SeaKing SK-B03</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Crafted for anglers who appreciate tradition and quality, the SeaKing SK-B01 and SK-B03 fiberglass </span><span>bait boards feature a UV resistant PE plastic cutting board, a convenient sink with drain for storage, </span><span>and robust 316 marine grade stainless steel hardware. These boards are meticulously handmade </span><span>using top-grade composite materials for durability and reliability on the water. Ideal for serious </span><span>fishermen, these bait boards offer exceptional functionality and enduring craftsmanship, ensuring they </span><span>stand up to the rigors of marine environments while providing essential features for a successful day </span><span>of fishing.</span><strong></strong></p>",
